"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Skip Go (`regular deposit`)\\n\\nSkip Go API is a **universal interoperability platform**, allowing **seamless swaps and transfers** across multiple blockchain ecosystems via **bridges such as CCTP and Axelar**.\\n\\n## Supported Chains & Assets\\n\\n- **Chains:** Ethereum Mainnet, Arbitrum, Avalanche, Base, Optimism, Polygon, Solana, and Cosmos chains\\n- **Assets:** USDC, ETH, POL\\n\\n## Min & Max Transfer Sizes\\n\\n| Source Chain     | Min Transfer (USD) | Max Transfer (USD) |\\n| ---------------- | ------------------ | ------------------ |\\n| Ethereum Mainnet | \\\\~$0.05            | \\\\~$1,000,000       |\\n| Other EVM Chains | \\\\~$0.05            | \\\\~$1,000,000       |\\n| Solana           | \\\\~$0.05            | \\\\~$1,000,000       |\\n| Cosmos Chains    | \\\\~$0.05            | \\\\~$1,000,000       |\\n\\n## Fees  \\nSource chain gas fees \\\\+ Deposits \\\\~$0.02 Withdrawals: \\\\~$0.1-$7\\n\\n| Source Chain     | Fee (USD)                               |\\n| ---------------- | --------------------------------------- |\\n| Ethereum Mainnet | Deposits \\\\~$0.02 Withdrawals: \\\\~$0.1-$7 |\\n| Other EVM Chains | Deposits \\\\~$0.02 Withdrawals: \\\\~$0.1-$7 |\\n| Solana           | Deposits \\\\~$0.02 Withdrawals: \\\\~$0.1-$7 |\\n| Cosmos Chains    | Deposits \\\\~$0.02 Withdrawals: \\\\~$0.1-$7 |\\n\\n## Process Flow (Deposit)\\n\\n1. **Connect your wallet** to the dYdX interface and navigate to the \\\"Deposit\\\" section\\n2. **Enter the amount** you wish to transfer (First time 1.25 USDC will be kept in wallet for gas fees)\\n3. **Choose source chain and asset** you wish to deposit\\n4. **Review the transaction details** including estimated fees and finality time\\n5. **Confirm and sign** the transaction from your wallet\\n6. **Third-party protocol interactions begin:**\\n   - If your source token is not USDC, an automatic swap occurs via integrated DEXs\\n   - Funds are sent to bridge contracts (CCTP, Axelar, etc.) based on optimal route\\n   - These bridges rely on external validators and relayers to verify cross-chain transactions\\n7. **Wait for confirmation** across all involved networks (may take 10-20 minutes)\\n   - Multiple relayer networks and validators must reach consensus\\n   - Each bridge and network has its own finality period\\n8. **Once confirmed**, funds are available in your dYdX account\\n   - Relayers monitor and trigger the final IBC transfer to dYdX Chain\\n\\n## Example Deposit\\nEthereum → dYdX via Skip Go\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n    \\\"operations\\\": [\\n        {\\n            \\\"cctp_transfer\\\": {\\n                \\\"from_chain_id\\\": \\\"1\\\",\\n                \\\"to_chain_id\\\": \\\"noble-1\\\",\\n                \\\"denom_in\\\": \\\"USDC\\\",\\n                \\\"denom_out\\\": \\\"uusdc\\\",\\n                \\\"bridge_id\\\": \\\"CCTP\\\"\\n            }\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"transfer\\\": {\\n                \\\"from_chain_id\\\": \\\"noble-1\\\",\\n                \\\"to_chain_id\\\": \\\"dydx-mainnet-1\\\",\\n                \\\"denom_in\\\": \\\"uusdc\\\",\\n                \\\"denom_out\\\": \\\"ibc/USDC\\\",\\n                \\\"bridge_id\\\": \\\"IBC\\\"\\n            }\\n        }\\n    ]\\n}\\n```\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo#skip-go-regular-deposit\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>Skip Go API is a <strong>universal interoperability platform</strong>, allowing <strong>seamless swaps and transfers</strong> across multiple blockchain ecosystems via <strong>bridges such as CCTP and Axelar</strong>.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo.mdx#skip-go-regular-deposit\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nSkip Go API is a universal interoperability platform, allowing seamless swaps and transfers across multiple blockchain ecosystems via bridges such as CCTP and Axelar.\\n\",\"title\":\"Skip Go (regular deposit)\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo#supported-chains--assets\",\"html\":\"\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Chains:</strong> Ethereum Mainnet, Arbitrum, Avalanche, Base, Optimism, Polygon, Solana, and Cosmos chains</li>\\n<li><strong>Assets:</strong> USDC, ETH, POL</li>\\n</ul>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo.mdx#supported-chains--assets\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nChains: Ethereum Mainnet, Arbitrum, Avalanche, Base, Optimism, Polygon, Solana, and Cosmos chains\\nAssets: USDC, ETH, POL\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Supported Chains &amp; Assets\",\"titles\":[\"Skip Go (regular deposit)\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo#min--max-transfer-sizes\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Source Chain</th><th>Min Transfer (USD)</th><th>Max Transfer (USD)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Ethereum Mainnet</td><td>~$0.05</td><td>~$1,000,000</td></tr><tr><td>Other EVM Chains</td><td>~$0.05</td><td>~$1,000,000</td></tr><tr><td>Solana</td><td>~$0.05</td><td>~$1,000,000</td></tr><tr><td>Cosmos Chains</td><td>~$0.05</td><td>~$1,000,000</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo.mdx#min--max-transfer-sizes\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nSource ChainMin Transfer (USD)Max Transfer (USD)Ethereum Mainnet~$0.05~$1,000,000Other EVM Chains~$0.05~$1,000,000Solana~$0.05~$1,000,000Cosmos Chains~$0.05~$1,000,000\\n\",\"title\":\"Min &amp; Max Transfer Sizes\",\"titles\":[\"Skip Go (regular deposit)\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo#fees\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Source chain gas fees + Deposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7</p>\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Source Chain</th><th>Fee (USD)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Ethereum Mainnet</td><td>Deposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7</td></tr><tr><td>Other EVM Chains</td><td>Deposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7</td></tr><tr><td>Solana</td><td>Deposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7</td></tr><tr><td>Cosmos Chains</td><td>Deposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo.mdx#fees\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nSource chain gas fees + Deposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7\\nSource ChainFee (USD)Ethereum MainnetDeposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7Other EVM ChainsDeposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7SolanaDeposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7Cosmos ChainsDeposits ~$0.02 Withdrawals: ~$0.1-$7\\n\",\"title\":\"Fees\",\"titles\":[\"Skip Go (regular deposit)\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo#process-flow-deposit\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li><strong>Connect your wallet</strong> to the dYdX interface and navigate to the &quot;Deposit&quot; section</li>\\n<li><strong>Enter the amount</strong> you wish to transfer (First time 1.25 USDC will be kept in wallet for gas fees)</li>\\n<li><strong>Choose source chain and asset</strong> you wish to deposit</li>\\n<li><strong>Review the transaction details</strong> including estimated fees and finality time</li>\\n<li><strong>Confirm and sign</strong> the transaction from your wallet</li>\\n<li>\\n<strong>Third-party protocol interactions begin:</strong>\\n<ul>\\n<li>If your source token is not USDC, an automatic swap occurs via integrated DEXs</li>\\n<li>Funds are sent to bridge contracts (CCTP, Axelar, etc.) based on optimal route</li>\\n<li>These bridges rely on external validators and relayers to verify cross-chain transactions</li>\\n</ul>\\n</li>\\n<li><strong>Wait for confirmation</strong> across all involved networks (may take 10-20 minutes)\\n<ul>\\n<li>Multiple relayer networks and validators must reach consensus</li>\\n<li>Each bridge and network has its own finality period</li>\\n</ul>\\n</li>\\n<li><strong>Once confirmed</strong>, funds are available in your dYdX account\\n<ul>\\n<li>Relayers monitor and trigger the final IBC transfer to dYdX Chain</li>\\n</ul>\\n</li>\\n</ol>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo.mdx#process-flow-deposit\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nConnect your wallet to the dYdX interface and navigate to the &quot;Deposit&quot; section\\nEnter the amount you wish to transfer (First time 1.25 USDC will be kept in wallet for gas fees)\\nChoose source chain and asset you wish to deposit\\nReview the transaction details including estimated fees and finality time\\nConfirm and sign the transaction from your wallet\\n\\nThird-party protocol interactions begin:\\n\\nIf your source token is not USDC, an automatic swap occurs via integrated DEXs\\nFunds are sent to bridge contracts (CCTP, Axelar, etc.) based on optimal route\\nThese bridges rely on external validators and relayers to verify cross-chain transactions\\n\\n\\nWait for confirmation across all involved networks (may take 10-20 minutes)\\n\\nMultiple relayer networks and validators must reach consensus\\nEach bridge and network has its own finality period\\n\\n\\nOnce confirmed, funds are available in your dYdX account\\n\\nRelayers monitor and trigger the final IBC transfer to dYdX Chain\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Process Flow (Deposit)\",\"titles\":[\"Skip Go (regular deposit)\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo#example-deposit\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Ethereum → dYdX via Skip Go</p>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">{</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">    &quot;operations&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: [</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">        {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">            &quot;cctp_transfer&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;from_chain_id&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;1&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;to_chain_id&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;noble-1&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;denom_in&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;USDC&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;denom_out&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;uusdc&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;bridge_id&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;CCTP&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">            }</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">        },</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">        {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">            &quot;transfer&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;from_chain_id&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;noble-1&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;to_chain_id&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;dydx-mainnet-1&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;denom_in&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;uusdc&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;denom_out&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;ibc/USDC&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">                &quot;bridge_id&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;IBC&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">            }</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">        }</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    ]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}</span></span></code></pre>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/deposits-withdrawals/skipgo.mdx#example-deposit\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nEthereum → dYdX via Skip Go\\n{\\n    &quot;operations&quot;: [\\n        {\\n            &quot;cctp_transfer&quot;: {\\n                &quot;from_chain_id&quot;: &quot;1&quot;,\\n                &quot;to_chain_id&quot;: &quot;noble-1&quot;,\\n                &quot;denom_in&quot;: &quot;USDC&quot;,\\n                &quot;denom_out&quot;: &quot;uusdc&quot;,\\n                &quot;bridge_id&quot;: &quot;CCTP&quot;\\n            }\\n        },\\n        {\\n            &quot;transfer&quot;: {\\n                &quot;from_chain_id&quot;: &quot;noble-1&quot;,\\n                &quot;to_chain_id&quot;: &quot;dydx-mainnet-1&quot;,\\n                &quot;denom_in&quot;: &quot;uusdc&quot;,\\n                &quot;denom_out&quot;: &quot;ibc/USDC&quot;,\\n                &quot;bridge_id&quot;: &quot;IBC&quot;\\n            }\\n        }\\n    ]\\n}\",\"title\":\"Example Deposit\",\"titles\":[\"Skip Go (regular deposit)\"]}]}}"
